biography.placeOfBirth: Autonomous City of Buenos Aires, Argentina
biography.bio: Alejandro Fiore was born on July 5, 1969 in Autonomous City of Buenos Aires, Argentina. He is an actor and writer, known for Green Waters (2009), Tocá para mí (2001) and A Oeste do Fim do Mundo (2013).
biography.name: Alejandro Fiore

biography.bio: Juliana Giuliani is an actress, known for El abismo... todavía estamos (2011).
biography.name: Juliana Giuliani

biography.bio: Juan Palomino was born on July 6, 1961. He is an actor and director, known for Mujeres de nadie (2007), Diablo (2011) and Kryptonite (2015). He has been married to Lucila Robirosa since June 13, 2001. They have one child.
biography.name: Juan Palomino

biography.bio: Sponatneous, friendly, and loved actress of Argentinian show business, Mabel Pessen started her career in the beginning of the 60s. She has played many characters as a distinguished supporting actress. In 1973, She got a bit part in the soap opera "Pobre Diabla" written by Alberto Migre, but her good and remarkable performance kept her working until the end of it. Writer Alberto Migre said "It has always been a pleasure to work with Mabel Pessen". In fact, many of her performances used to appear in Alberto Migre's soap operas.
biography.name: Mabel Pessen

biography.bio: Agustina Posse is an actress, known for Montaña rusa, otra vuelta (1995), Calientes (2000) and Gasoleros (1998).
biography.name: Agustina Posse

biography.bio: Betty Raiter is known for her work on El abismo... todavía estamos (2011), Asado para tres (1986) and The History of Argentine Tennis (2006).
biography.name: Betty Raiter

biography.bio: Raúl Rizzo was born on June 18, 1948 in Argentina. He is an actor, known for The Strange Lady (1989), Sos mi hombre (2012) and Cosecharás tu siembra (1991).
biography.name: Raúl Rizzo

biography.bio: Adriana Salonia has played many supporting and main characters since she started her career in 1986 in the movie" La Noche de los Lapices". Later, she was one of the main character in the successful show "Socorro Quinto Año" (1989). In 1990, she played an outstanding supporting role in the soap opera written by Alberto Migre" Una Voz en el Telefono" with Raul Taibo, Carolina Papaleo, Dulio Marzio, Elizabeth Killian, and Adriana Gardizabal. Since the 90s, Salonia has appeared in several films, soap operas, and other television series such as "Alta Comedia" (1991) where she appeared in the episode "Todos Juntos Como Antes" with leading actors Rodolfo Beban, Dora Baret, and Delfy De Ortega. Currently,Adriana salonia is rehearsing for the movie "La Mitad Negada".
biography.name: Adriana Salonia

biography.bio: Ismael Santillán is an actor, known for First Mission (2010), Manhunt (2008) and Los del suelo (2015).
biography.name: Ismael Santillán

biography.bio: Humberto Serrano was born in Spain. He was an actor, known for Son of the Bride (2001), Antonella (1991) and Alén, luz de luna (1996). He died on January 21, 2013 in Buenos Aires, Argentina.
biography.name: Humberto Serrano

biography.bio: Daniel Valenzuela is an actor and writer, known for Crane World (1999), La león (2007) and Burnt Money (2000).
biography.name: Daniel Valenzuela

biography.bio: Adrián Yospe was born on February 12, 1970 in Buenos Aires, Argentina. He was an actor, known for Pizza, Beer, and Cigarettes (1998), Wild Horses (1995) and 5.5.5 (2013). He died on November 10, 2011 in San Isidro City, San Isidro, Buenos Aires.
biography.name: Adrián Yospe

biography.bio: Pablo Yotich is an actor and director, known for El abismo... todavía estamos (2011), Almas de Furia and Cuatro de copas (2012).
biography.name: Pablo Yotich

biography.bio: Gabriel Zuccarini is an actor, known for Vivir intentando (2003), Avellaneda's Moon (2004) and Los superagentes, nueva generación (2008).
biography.name: Gabriel Zuccarini
